    "persona_panel": "AI Persona chat gicaa - engage i authentic conversations ki historical figures, scientists, literary characters, onyo custom personas. Uses advanced AI i simulate period-accurate speech kit, knowledge, ki perspectives. Perfect pi primary source analysis, perspective-taking, ki empathy-building exercises. Supports multiple response modes: I-Character (fully immersive), Educational (ki learning scaffolds), onyo Mixed (balanced approach).",
    "persona_card": "AI persona ready pi conversation. lwak card nyutu character's nying, kare period, ki expertise area. Dii i cak interview - AI will respond authentically based wi their historical context, beliefs, ki knowledge. Tii personas pi primary source analysis, perspective-taking exercises, onyo creative coyo inspiration.",
    "persona_generate_button": "Generate AI personas automatically ki bot mamegi source content. system analyzes mamegi text i niang key figures, historical periods, onyo character archetypes ki creates authentic conversational partners. Yene personas include accurate biographical details, period-appropriate vocabulary, ki contextual knowledge limitations (they won't know pi events after their kare).",
    "persona_select_button": "Yer man persona i begin mamegi interview onyo conversation. Once selected, in'll donyo immersive chat interface kwene in can ask lapeny, explore their perspective, ki earn XP pi meaningful exchanges. AI responds based wi character's historical knowledge, personality, ki cultural context.",
    "persona_back_btn": "Return i persona selection gicaa i yer different character. mamegi current conversation progress tye automatically gigwokki, ki in can return i mede it later. man allows exploring multiple perspectives wi rom historical lok.",
    "persona_custom_instructions": "Med mukene requirements pi how persona should behave during conversations. Examples: focus wi mukene kare period, emphasize certain beliefs onyo values, maintain particular speech kit, onyo limit responses i historically accurate knowledge. lapwony can tii man i align personas ki mukene learning objectives.",
    "persona_response_mode": "Yer how persona responds i create different learning experiences. IN CHARACTER: Fully immersive historical voice ki no modern explanations. EDUCATIONAL: Character speaks ento includes learning scaffolds, vocabulary support, ki context. MIXED: Balanced approach ki authentic voice plus occasional clarifications. Yer based wi latin kwan readiness ki learning goals.",
    "persona_free_response": "Type mamegi own yab-ended response instead pa selecting ki bot pre-written options. Free response mode promotes creative expression, critical thinking, ki authentic dialogue skills. Responses tye analyzed pi historical atir, empathy, ki depth pa inquiry. Higher-quality lapeny earn mapol XP.",
    "persona_hints_toggle": "Nyut onyo kan response suggestions ki conversation hints. ka enabled, system provides scaffolded lapeny starters, historical context lok ma tito, ki engagement suggestions. Helpful pi latin kwan manyen i historical inquiry onyo those needing support ki yab-ended questioning. lapwony can disable hints pi mapol advanced assessment scenarios.",
    "persona_show_hints": "Nyutu helpful hints pi engaging ki persona. Hints include historically relevant lapeny i ask, topics character would find interesting, ki lok ma tito meno lead i deeper understanding. Maber pi latin kwan who need scaffolding onyo aren't sure how i begin historical interview.",
    "persona_submit_btn": "Cwal mamegi message i persona character. mamegi lapeny onyo response tye analyzed pi relevance ki depth. AI persona will respond authentically based wi their historical context, knowledge, ki personality. Well-crafted lapeny meno nyut historical understanding earn bonus XP.",
    "persona_close": "Lor persona conversation gicaa. mamegi chat history ki earned XP tye automatically gigwokki. in can resume man conversation later ki bot History tab.",
    "persona_close_title": "Lor Persona Chat",
    "persona_reflection_input": "Coyo mamegi reflection wi conversation pi assessment. Reflect wi ngo in learned pi historical figure, how their perspective differs ki bot modern viewpoints, ki how man conversation changed mamegi understanding. Reflections tye evaluated using rubric aligned i historical thinking skills ki can earn significant XP.",
    "persona_conclude": "End conversation ki generate comprehensive tyenlok pa mamegi discussion. tyenlok includes: key topics covered, historical insights gained, quality pa mamegi lapeny, empathy demonstrated, ki XP earned. man tyenlok can be exported pi assessment, added i latin kwan portfolios, onyo used as coyo prompt pi reflection activities.",
    "persona_save_chat": "Gwoki man conversation i review onyo share later. Saved chats preserve tyek dialogue, XP earned, timestamps, ki any reflections. Tii gigwokki chats pi latin kwan portfolios, assessment caden, kilas discussions, onyo exemplar models. Saved conversations can be exported as PDF onyo shared ki okene latin kwan.",
    "persona_topic_spark": "Get conversation starter onyo lok suggestion ka in're pe sure ngo i ask. system generates historically relevant lapeny based wi persona's background, expertise, ki kare period. Maber pi overcoming writer's block onyo discovering manyen angles i explore i mamegi historical inquiry.",
    "persona_auto_send": "Automatically cwal mamegi message ka in juk typing pi few nyere. Creates mapol natural conversational flow, especially ka using voice dictation. Disable man ka in prefer i review ki loko messages before sending, onyo ka in need mapol kare i compose thoughtful responses.",
    "analysis_generate_button": "Analyze mamegi source text pi reading level, complexity, ki features.",
    "analysis_check_accuracy": "Fact-check source content against reliable references.",
    "outline_generate_button": "Generate visual organizer ki bot mamegi source content.",
    "timeline_generate_button": "Generate timeline pa events ki bot mamegi source content.",
    "timeline_topic": "main lok onyo theme pa timeline being yene. AI creates historically accurate events based wi man lok ki mamegi source content. Example topics: American Revolution, Life Cycle pa Stars, Shakespeare's Career. Events tye automatically ordered chronologically pi sequencing practice.",
    "timeline_count": "wel pa events i include i timeline. mapol events create longer, mapol detailed timelines ento increase difficulty. Recommended: 4-6 events pi beginners, 8-10 pi intermediate, 12+ pi advanced lupwonye. Events tye draggable pi sequencing practice after kwo.",
