      "assessment_checklist": "☑ Checklist me pim",
      "per_grade_skills_checklists_use_during": "Checklist me twero me kwan acel acel. Tii i kare me pim ngat-ki-ngat onyo me yubo pwony.",
      "my_child_says_i_hate_fractions": "Latina waco ni \"Akwero bute\"",
      "very_common_fractions_break_the_rules_": "Nen loyo. Bute turo cik ma lutin kwan gipwonyo pi namba mupong — namba madito pe te lok kare ducu ni dit. Akemo obeddo ada ki me atir. Kony ki: (1) tic ki model ma nen macalo pizza onyo line me bute, (2) kube ki kwo ada (tedo, saa, cente), (3) tego manok ki mapol (dakika 5 i nino) pe session malac, (4) pwoc tego, pe gam maber keken.",
      "my_child_doesn_t_understand_why_proced": "Latina pe niaŋ PIŊO yoo tiyo",
      "they_are_not_alone_most_students_learn": "Pe gikeken — lutin kwan mapol gipwonyo yoo mukwongo ka piŋo lacen. Kony ki nyuto kare ducu kit ma yoo nen ki cal. \"Anyim 3/4 ki 1/2\" twero goyo macalo rectangle. Tab me Op Proofs timo man pigi. Peny \"piŋo?\" mot ki mapol.",
      "how_can_i_help_with_homework_without_d": "Atwero konyo homework nining ma pe atiyo pigi?",
      "use_the_worked_examples_tab_they_show_": "Tii ki tab me Worked Examples — nyuto yoo kir ki kir ki niang. Wot ki i peko ma rwatte kacel, pe acel-lu. Ka giwaco \"Pe angeyo kit me cakke,\" peny \"Peko openyo ni ingony ango? Ngo ma wangeyo?\" System me anyut i Peko me Lok miyo anyut me layer — tem mukwongo ma peya gam.",
      "what_should_i_drill": "Ango ma amyero atego?",
      "ies_practice_guide_recommends_1_magnit": "IES Practice Guide tiro: (1) tam me dit (tic me line me namba), (2) kube i kin ma nen ki lanyut, (3) peko me lok i lok. KWER: tego i yoo ma pe niang. Tii dakika 5 i Benchmark Trainer, 5 i Peko me Lok, ki 5 i tuk — meno obeddo session me dakika 15 maber.",
      "my_child_gets_the_procedure_right_but_": "Latina timo yoo atir ento gam obeddo maraco",
      "usually_means_a_small_arithmetic_error": "Kare ducu te lok bal matidi me matematik (labol, oanyim maraco) onyo pe oyot. Nyut Cheat Sheet — gitwero roto tic gi kir ki kir. Cuk gi me moko ki yo mukene (pim mukwongo, onyo tii ki model mukene).",
      "what_if_i_don_t_remember_fractions_wel": "Ka an kena pe apo bute maber?",
      "you_don_t_have_to_be_the_expert_use_th": "Pe myero ibed lalony! Tii ki Tab Guide ki Worked Examples — tiro yoo maleng. Maber loyo: nyut \"wek wanong man kacel.\" Itwero pwonyo kacel ki latina. Tab me Vocabulary konyo bene bot ludito.",
      "how_do_i_know_if_my_child_is_on_track": "Angeyo nining ni latina tye i yoo atir?",
      "look_at_the_standards_tab_to_see_which": "Nen tab me Standards me neno standard me CCSS ma gimyero gineye pi kwan gi. Tab me Mastery nyuto dongo. Pi rot oyotoyot: gitwero (a) goyo model pi 3/4, (b) waco bute marom ki 1/2, (c) poro 2/3 ki 3/4 ki tiro? Test adek meno gimako gin ma gigeno mapol me bute me K-5.",
      "parent_guide": "👨‍👩‍👧 Ganyo me lanyodo",
